author: Tom D'Angelo
title: FSU's Reggie Northrup looking for more success against Miami
text:
Florida State linebacker Reggie Northrup pondered the question, then did his best not to create bulletin board material.
“It’s not really a big deal,” Northrup said about his decision to flip from Miami to Florida State on signing day in 2012. “It’s great I never lost to the team that I decommitted from. You don’t want that to happen, things to be rubbed in your face.”
